TCP Vendor Crawlers¶

This module contains all vendor crawlers of TCP implementations. Available enumerations include:

TCP_Checksum

TCP Checksum [*]

TCP_MPTCPOption

Multipath TCP options [†]

TCP_Option

TCP Option Kind Numbers

TCP Checksum¶

This module contains the vendor crawler for TCP Checksum, which is automatically generating pcapkit.const.tcp.checksum.Checksum.
